content: I'm actually thinking of going for a more bohemian vibe, with lots of natural textures and earthy tones. I've been browsing through Target's home decor section, and I've also been eyeing some outdoor patio furniture to update my backyard. By the way, have you heard about The Vintage Closet? I've been going there a lot lately, and I always find some unique pieces that add a touch of personality to my space.
